text: Dabanwala railway station or Daban Wala railway station (Urdu and ) is located in Dabanwala village, Toba Tek Singh district of Punjab province, Pakistan. ==See also== * List of railway stations in Pakistan * Pakistan Railways ==References== ==External links== *Official Web Site of Pakistan Railways Category:Railway stations in Toba Tek Singh District Category:Railway stations on Khanewal–Wazirabad Line
